Package: biscuiteer
Type: Package
Title: a bunch of convenience functions for Biscuit
Description: A test harness for bsseq loading of Biscuit output, summarization
             of WGBS data over defined regions and in mappable samples, with or
             without imputation, dropping of mostly-NA rows, age estimates, etc.
Version: 0.9.75
Date: 2018-09-24
Author: Tim Triche, Jr. [aut, cre], Wanding Zhou [aut], Lyong Heo [ctb]
Maintainer: Tim Triche, Jr. <tim.triche@vai.org>
URL: https://github.com/trichelab/biscuiteer
BugReports: https://github.com/trichelab/biscuiteer/issues
License: Gnu GPL
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0), 
         bsseq
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: readr,
         qualV,
         Matrix, 
         impute,
         HDF5Array,
         S4Vectors, 
         Rsamtools,
         Biostrings, 
         data.table,
         GenomicRanges,
         VariantAnnotation,
         DelayedMatrixStats,
         Homo.sapiens,
         matrixStats,
         fastseg,
         HMMcopy,
         dmrseq,
         gtools
Suggests: DSS, 
          covr,
